00:35:53.550 --> 00:35:54.550
Someone died!

00:35:55.360 --> 00:35:56.840
-Someone died!
-Someone died!

00:35:56.840 --> 00:35:57.800
Someone fell into a well

00:35:57.800 --> 00:35:58.730
and was drowned.

00:36:00.110 --> 00:36:00.770
Where is it?

00:36:01.110 --> 00:36:02.550
J-Just over there.

00:36:04.630 --> 00:36:05.360
Lead the way!

00:36:08.960 --> 00:36:09.400
Officer,

00:36:09.400 --> 00:36:10.280
it's that well.

00:36:10.510 --> 00:36:11.440
Those who are irrelevant
should step aside!

00:36:11.440 --> 00:36:12.100
Step aside!

00:36:12.230 --> 00:36:12.890
Step aside!

00:36:13.150 --> 00:36:13.840
Step aside!

00:36:14.000 --> 00:36:14.760
Let the officer take a look.

00:36:14.760 --> 00:36:15.230
Jia!

00:36:15.510 --> 00:36:16.040
Xue Huan!

00:36:17.480 --> 00:36:19.190
Onlookers, stay 3 zhang away!

00:36:19.280 --> 00:36:19.880
Step back!

00:36:29.030 --> 00:36:29.480
Hurry!

00:36:31.110 --> 00:36:31.760
The coroner is here.

00:36:31.760 --> 00:36:32.890
The coroner is here.

00:36:34.190 --> 00:36:35.320
The coroner is here.

00:36:36.880 --> 00:36:38.410
Examine the corpse at once.

00:36:38.440 --> 00:36:38.800
Yes.

00:36:42.000 --> 00:36:42.530
How is it?

00:36:44.510 --> 00:36:45.630
There are scrape marks

00:36:45.630 --> 00:36:47.840
from bricks and stones on the face.

00:36:48.590 --> 00:36:50.710
In the hair and under the fingernails,

00:36:50.710 --> 00:36:51.480
there's mud and sand.

00:36:51.480 --> 00:36:53.810
It indicates that he was drowned to death.

00:36:54.400 --> 00:36:56.830
In terms of the states
of his hands and eyes,

00:36:57.150 --> 00:36:59.110
if he had jumped into the well by himself,

00:36:59.110 --> 00:37:01.920
his eyes would be closed
with clenched fists.

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:04.320
If he had accidentally
fallen into the well,

00:37:04.320 --> 00:37:07.250
his eyes would be slightly open
with curled fingers.

00:37:07.320 --> 00:37:10.190
But if he had been pushed into the well
by someone else,

00:37:10.190 --> 00:37:13.000
his eyes would be slightly open
with curled fingers, too.

00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:15.320
Unfortunately, there are so many
pedestrians coming and going here.

00:37:15.320 --> 00:37:16.960
The scene has been badly ruined.

00:37:16.960 --> 00:37:18.220
It can't be determined

00:37:18.230 --> 00:37:19.480
whether the victim fell into it by himself

00:37:19.480 --> 00:37:21.540
or was pushed into it by someone else.

00:37:22.330 --> 00:37:23.930
What about the time of death?

00:37:24.150 --> 00:37:25.760
It was after 11 PM.

00:37:26.920 --> 00:37:29.400
The main streets
were under curfew late at night,

00:37:29.400 --> 00:37:30.360
but inside the district,

00:37:30.360 --> 00:37:31.820
people could move freely.

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:33.520
He was still outside at 11 PM.

00:37:34.480 --> 00:37:37.480
I think he had spent time
at a restaurant for pleasure.

00:37:37.510 --> 00:37:38.240
Captain Xue!

00:37:40.360 --> 00:37:40.820
Mentor.

00:37:41.000 --> 00:37:42.190
From now on, in official occasions,

00:37:42.190 --> 00:37:43.390
don't call me Mentor.

00:37:43.880 --> 00:37:44.280
Yes.

00:37:45.550 --> 00:37:47.110
Official Lu, what can I do for you?

00:37:47.110 --> 00:37:48.710
Go investigate the restaurants
and music clubs

00:37:48.710 --> 00:37:50.110
inside the Shengye District.

00:37:50.110 --> 00:37:50.880
I've investigated them.

00:37:50.880 --> 00:37:53.140
Only one of them stayed open at midnight.

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:55.690
Captain Xue, you got prepared in advance?

00:37:55.840 --> 00:37:56.840
After I took up the post of captain,

00:37:56.840 --> 00:37:58.000
this is my first day doing this job.

00:37:58.000 --> 00:37:59.360
How would I dare to be careless?

00:37:59.360 --> 00:38:00.840
I've asked someone
to tell the restaurant's owner,

00:38:00.840 --> 00:38:01.370
servants

00:38:01.550 --> 00:38:02.360
and pipa players

00:38:02.360 --> 00:38:03.670
to come here and identify the corpse.

00:38:03.670 --> 00:38:05.400
And I've ordered some men
to search the streets

00:38:05.400 --> 00:38:07.060
and check for missing people.

00:38:10.070 --> 00:38:10.670
Very good.

00:38:11.670 --> 00:38:12.400
Official Lu!

00:38:12.630 --> 00:38:14.510
I've brought the restaurant's owner here!

00:38:14.510 --> 00:38:16.230
I've brought Kuai Wu's wife here!

00:38:16.230 --> 00:38:17.800
This child is so pitiful.

00:38:19.480 --> 00:38:20.710
Honey!

00:38:22.800 --> 00:38:24.510
-Honey!
-Father!

00:38:24.550 --> 00:38:25.070
Father!

00:38:25.230 --> 00:38:28.190
How did you fall into the well?

00:38:28.190 --> 00:38:29.000
Father!

00:38:29.840 --> 00:38:31.800
Honey!

00:38:33.220 --> 00:38:34.900
[Chengfo Temple]

00:38:35.130 --> 00:38:38.650
[Chengfo Temple]

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:45.900
Why isn't Wu Yang here yet?

00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:47.440
We agreed to meet at 9 AM.

00:38:47.510 --> 00:38:49.030
It's almost 10 AM now,

00:38:49.110 --> 00:38:50.630
but there's still no sign of her.

00:38:50.630 --> 00:38:52.710
Amitabha.

00:38:55.670 --> 00:38:58.190
This must be Miss Xijun!

00:38:58.590 --> 00:39:00.450
Greetings, Buddhist Guangxiao.

00:39:02.360 --> 00:39:04.190
If I'm not mistaken,

00:39:04.190 --> 00:39:05.320
this must be...

00:39:06.360 --> 00:39:07.520
Madam Shiliu!

00:39:09.510 --> 00:39:10.710
Buddhist Guangxiao.

00:39:10.760 --> 00:39:12.090
You're still mistaken.

00:39:12.190 --> 00:39:13.290
I'm not Shiliu.

00:39:13.480 --> 00:39:14.210
I'm Yingtao.

00:39:16.070 --> 00:39:17.410
Madam Yingtao!

00:39:17.510 --> 00:39:19.320
It's been almost a year since we last met.

00:39:19.320 --> 00:39:21.150
Are you two
visiting the Chengfo Temple today

00:39:21.150 --> 00:39:22.280
to offer incense?

00:39:22.480 --> 00:39:23.710
How wonderful.

00:39:24.110 --> 00:39:25.150
Come on. Please come inside now.

00:39:25.150 --> 00:39:26.840
I'll accompany you personally.

00:39:26.840 --> 00:39:27.760
I'm sorry.

00:39:28.070 --> 00:39:30.000
We'll come again another day
to offer incense.

00:39:30.000 --> 00:39:33.000
Today, we're going to
visit the Qu River with a friend.

00:39:35.280 --> 00:39:37.190
It turns out you're waiting for someone.

00:39:37.190 --> 00:39:38.760
Please make yourselves comfortable.

00:39:38.760 --> 00:39:40.890
Take your time to wait for your friend.

00:39:41.250 --> 00:39:45.850
[Chengfo Temple]

00:39:48.070 --> 00:39:49.070
Let's wait another 15 minutes.

00:39:49.070 --> 00:39:49.880
If she still doesn't come,

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:50.670
I won't

00:39:50.760 --> 00:39:52.360
be friends with her anymore.

00:39:54.800 --> 00:39:56.400
Maybe her mother is strict with her

00:39:56.400 --> 00:39:57.800
and doesn't let her come out.

00:39:57.800 --> 00:39:58.880
Just be a little more patient.